{"word":"λάκκος","slug":"λάκκος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λάκκος</b></el> <el>(λάκκος, ὁ,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a pond</i> for water-fowl, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> vivarium, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a pit, reservoir</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}